"collapse panel-collapse"id="collapseThree"><div class="panel-body"><p>We offer all our customers ultimate peace of mind. We have you covered 100% on every eligible purchase. Visit the <a href="terms"rel="noopener"target="_blank"><strong>Buyer Policy Page</strong></a> to learn more.</p></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title"data-target="#collapseFour"data-toggle="collapse"><span>4.</span> What is the estimated delivery time?</h4></div><div class="collapse panel-collapse"id="collapseFour"><div class="panel-body"><p>DayDone delivers products to customers all over Nigeria. Same day delivery in Ibadan, Lagos 2-5, Rivers 3-6, Abuja 3-8 & other states 4-7 days</p></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title"data-target="#collapseFive"data-toggle="collapse"><span>5.</span> Why does the estimated delivery time vary?</h4></div><div class="collapse panel-collapse"id="collapseFive"><div class="panel-body"><p>DayDone is a agric/food product online marketplace that empowers Nigerians across the country. This means that not all products on DayDone are sold or delivered by DayDone. In addition, DayDone buyers and sellers are found in every state in Nigeria helping the farmers in the distribution of their produce. Given the various factors involved (the time it takes a get the produces from the farm, the courier company used, the distance between buyer and farmers, and more) delivery times may vary.</p></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title"data-target="#collapseSix"data-toggle="collapse"><span>6.</span>Can I return my product?</h4></div><div class="collapse panel-collapse"id="collapseSix"><div class="panel-body"><p>Yes, we have a flexible return policy for all produces, return and refund only applies during the grace period, product will only be accepted if their is no inflicted damage to the product after delivery. For perishable goods same day return while for non-perishable 2-4 days return grace without damage.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><script type="application/ld+json">{
